[ftp://downloads.netgear.com/files/314v320a.zip Latest firmware] (also usable with the [[Netgear RT314]])
[http://www.downloads.netgear.com/files/rt311ref.pdf Manual] The native OS for this device appears to be '''ZyNOS'''. The manufacturer is presumed to be '''ZyXEL'''. [http://www.bettina-attack.de/jonny/view.php/gadgets/soho_routers/ Gadgets - uClinux on SOHO routers] (good quality board images) :"Made in Taiwan", "Router-CBAD" and "P/N:45-401-000111" appears to be silkscreened on the board. The '''Samsung''' CPU used in this device has a P/N of S3C4500X01-QERO.
